products.name: 5-Year Standard Geek Squad Protection
products.shortDescription: Enhance your manufacturer warranty and get extended coverage when the warranty ends:We make house calls for failures from normal wear and tear. products.longDescription: You're excited to buy a new major appliance — now, make sure to protect it. Geek Squad Protection enhances your manufacturer warranty and gives you extended coverage when the warranty ends. Geek Squad Protection often covers important repairs that your manufacturer warranty doesn't (like failure due to a power surge). If something goes wrong after the manufacturer warranty ends, rest easy; you won't be stuck with a huge repair bill. Geek Squad Protection has your back and will take care of any covered repairs.
